data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadCaseCaseAssignment
data.value: select T1.NUMB, T1.STATUS, T1.CSE_OPEN_DATE, T1.NO_JURISDICTION_CD, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.SPD_ID, T2.OFF_ID, T2.OSP_CODE, T2.OSP_DATE from CKT_CASE T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_ASSIGN_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.NO_JURISDICTION_CD = ' ') and (T1.NUMB > @numb) and (T1.CSE_OPEN_DATE between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and (T1.NUMB = T2.CAS_NO) order by T1.NUMB, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE desc, T1.NUMB

data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN with(readuncommitted) where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select top(1) REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, CASES_OPN_W_ORDER, CASES_OPN_WO_ORDER from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel) and (REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId)

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, CASES_OPN_W_ORDER, CASES_OPN_WO_ORDER from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = 'JD')

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority35
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, CASES_OPN_W_ORDER = @casesOpnWOrder, CASES_OPN_WO_ORDER = @casesOpnWoOrder where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel) and (REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId)
